{"tid":1746778,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「警謊」誤導公眾話係佢地邀請紅十字會去理大","createTime":"2019-11-23T02:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T07:42:40.000Z","uid":68110,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4272413557d7fc255a067aec8cc39ff27bea71b","tid":1746778,"uid":68110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:09:07.000Z","msg":"國際醫學期刊《刺針》(The Lancet) 於網站內刊登了一名親身在 香港理工大學 提供救援的本地外科醫生 Darren Mann 的投稿。Darren 拆穿警謊，指警方當日誤導公眾 指是警方邀請紅十字會 到場，但事實是 Darren 那天早上聯絡紅十字會及無國界醫生，要求介入。<br />\n<br />\n他又指紅十字會到場之後等了兩個鐘，警方才批准他們進入理大，還限制救援時間，要求3小時內完成。紅十字會其後表示受傷人數眾多，要求延長救援時間。<br />\n<br />\n文中指警方對待救援的做法，遠低於 國際標準。拘捕義務急救員在文明國家 更是聞所未聞，違反人道主義。Darren 更強調這場是不文明戰爭 (Uncivil War) ，而阻礙義務救援，只會造成寒蟬效應，令義務急救員卻步。<br />\n<br />\n《The Lancet》：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flancet%2Farticle%2FPIIS0140-6736%2819&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvggDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=16ef1457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(19</a>)32909-5/fulltext#%20"},{"pid":"8ab83580ac15967469ed2647fd07191f0378408a","tid":1746778,"uid":68110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1O1i16x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1O1i16x.jpg&h=f8205d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e6e0ee6eba249f1c8f4568fa91aba6ca1b5f096f","tid":1746778,"uid":257683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:12:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744d717080c8026104ca30f5c18f1aa74e180a9b","tid":1746778,"uid":34487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:16:18.000Z","msg":"食屎警狗"},{"pid":"2e46790c6cc5ea8f5c91131e6ceca6bdb361e8eb","tid":1746778,"uid":681